{"tid":1757654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[最後8個鐘] 盡快登記做英國選民","createTime":"2019-11-26T15:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T23:46:48.000Z","uid":119277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de38e448d6a84d2763d04f0619abed210386ef6a","tid":1757654,"uid":119277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"香港場仗要打好耐，國際線必不可少，尤其要爭取英國關注香港狀況同埋BNO平權。<br />\n英國將喺12月大選，跪求以下兩類巴絲， 喺英國時間11月26號晚上11時59分前 ( 香港時間11月27號早上7點59分 ) 登記做選民! <br />\n<br />\n1.現時響英國<br />\n-英國公民或<br />\n-居住滿180日，持有BNO，British Dependent Territories，British overseas嘅香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9y%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=104f85b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a><br />\n<br />\n2.現時喺海外<br />\n英國公民-要過去15年內曾經登記過做選民需要有過去喺英國登記嘅住址，或<br />\n雙親/監護人響過去15年內喺英國有登記過，而你離開英國嘅時候未夠登記年齡登記，亦離開咗不多於15年<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/i-am-a/voter/overseas-voters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.electoralcommission.org.uk%2Fi-am-a%2Fvoter%2Foverseas-voters&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9y%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=b16d3945\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/i-am-a/voter/overseas-voters</a>"},{"pid":"8e37381c1190bb7e778162785d8b05272b749280","tid":1757654,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcc417f0be35be8d1d9e0e829c8bad01b74ba6ad","tid":1757654,"uid":119277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"自推&times;1"},{"pid":"e0eb3ce559f12df31da4d9e41b868a80ab897196","tid":1757654,"uid":119277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"自推&times;2"},{"pid":"f5cee4daf3cb4d34591e08b948815b99b9467732","tid":1757654,"uid":119277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0